Introduction

Sebin is a singer and lyricist in the boy group OMEGA X. He is signed with IPQ and was formerly in the boy group SNUPER.

On June 5, OMEGA X' label IPQ Entertainment revealed Sebin would be enlisting for his mandatory military service on July 16. The label further revealed Sebin is enlisting as an active-duty soldier.
